Package: ar0822-rpi-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms
Recommends: linux-headers-rpi-2712 | linux-headers-rpi-v8
Description: Onsemi AR0822 camera driver for Raspberry Pi (DKMS)
 Kernel module and device tree overlay for Onsemi AR0822, an 8 MP
 rolling shutter back side illuminated CMOS image sensor, on Raspberry Pi
 running a 6.12 or newer kernel.
 .
 The module is compiled on target with DKMS, so a single package works
 across Raspberry Pi OS releases and kernel updates. Installing the package
 also builds and installs ar0822 device tree overlay to /boot/overlays.
